# Layout of this directory:
#   *.csv          aggregated `*_summary.csv` files (one row per metric, from
#                  training/eval runs) + the published `paper_*.csv` reference
#                  numbers — the canonical "final metrics".
#   plots/         every generated figure (master bar/radial, risk frontier,
#                  sweep/quantile/atari PNGs).
#   sweeps/        archived sweep/study CSVs.
#   reform_a/      a self-contained reformation study (CSVs + COMPARISON.md).
#
# Raw per-UE evaluation CSVs are too large to track; everything else is checked
# in.
/*_raw.csv
